{"tid":1688814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈含淘寶殺蟲樂？含氯氰菊酯 cypermethrin神經毒素","createTime":"2019-11-02T14:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:32:58.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc6e11a49a1d557ad56b59e87a3345b3262c0708","tid":1688814,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/02/224622_2903f80e987b8e063d5e55a9ab1565fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F02%2F224622_2903f80e987b8e063d5e55a9ab1565fd.png&h=151e6692&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7174f9d052427150ac0272a66efb7510df73ee80","tid":1688814,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fc6b18e391ced248f17c91ba50118390eaab997","tid":1688814,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a9d54849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"01a8b90febec984b39c4f155807fc8e9cdd3066a","tid":1688814,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56dbed29c36e8ff2d292ad70d7417f03562316e7","tid":1688814,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"毒性 1.腦部與神經<br />\n除蟲菊精藥劑依其結構是否含有氰基(Cyano group)分成二群，對人體 之危害亦伴隨氰基之有無而具有差異，賽滅寧屬於 TypeII(含氰基)，會引發 興奮及抽搐，產生流涎及舞蹈症反應(choreoathetosis with salivation)。在 功能觀察組合實驗(FOB)中，SD 品系大鼠(Sprague&ndash;Dawley rats)攝入 100 及 200ppm 玉米油 4 小時後，即出現流涎、動作失調、蹣跚、自主活動減 少甚至死亡。另外在慢毒性處理組別中，大鼠食用含 111ppm 的飼料時，會 出現震顫、流涎、動作失調、蹣跚、不正常姿勢、後肢分岔等反應。根據特 羅夫頓及瑞特(Crofton and Reiter)的研究(1988)顯示，攝入賽滅寧的動物在 響聲驚嚇實驗(acoustic startle response)中其跳躍次數會增加，但跳躍的高 度會減少，其食物學習能力(food-reinforced learned behavior)會降低，記 憶力也會減退。"},{"pid":"75bc90d2948c0f13dc618b5efa1da9c99c3ce79d","tid":1688814,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"http://163.21.236.12/~fireant/epaper10202/Cypermethrin.pdf"},{"pid":"ffb3dd4257bc545e5cf163d29db9c1e7632751c7","tid":1688814,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />化武"},{"pid":"399b603357479e0d78ffbeae517db0facdf3a468","tid":1688814,"uid":264873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"#Twitter吹雞<br />\n<br />\n之峰將今日魔警暴行放哂上Twitter，請逐條tweet like &amp; retweet！<br />\n<br />\n如果有美議員或外媒報導，可以適當時候擺之峰嘅tweets落去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1190609673101012992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1190609673101012992&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a9620647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1190609673101012992&h=da9e9a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1190609673101012992</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FjYwE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FjYwE9.jpg&h=d9ea8d80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"095494b37c3e74d52f01f42858f3ada640aece6b","tid":1688814,"uid":303895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5858d10383dac4d058b5a5bd73609ea278829fe6","tid":1688814,"uid":303895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"解散衙差刻不容緩"},{"pid":"156b365c6910a217d03d78b8133eb2